'''''The Doobage''''' was a [[YT-1300 light freighter/Legends|YT-1300]] which was owned by [[HoloNet News/Legends|HoloNet News]] presenter [[Rogan B.B. Cham]]. The [[Starship/Legends|ship]] itself was painted in a pearlescent white [[Color/Legends|color]] with fluorescent pink and green headlights. The inside of the ship was retrofitted for Cham's job as a HoloNet News presenter with a camera set on the top of the cockpit and an editing suite in the cargo area. The ship was used by Cham to transport a group of [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebels]] into the [[Cynestra Space Craft Show]] by hiding them inside cargo, which was unloaded on the station.

